<h1>Confirm your email change</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @user.display_name %>,</p>

<p>Someone requested changing your Turf Monster email to <strong><%= @new_email %></strong>.</p>

<p>If this was you, confirm the change:</p>

<p><%= link_to "Confirm email change", @confirm_url %></p>

<p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:</p>
<p style="word-break:break-all;"><%= @confirm_url %></p>

<p>This link expires in 30 minutes. Until you confirm, your email stays
   <strong><%= @current_email %></strong> — no change has been made.</p>

<p>If this wasn't you, ignore this email — your account is unchanged. You may
   want to review your account security.</p>

<p>— Turf Monster</p>
